text: Kyle Evans Gay (born 1985/1986) is an American Democratic politician who has been the 27th and current Lieutenant Governor of Delaware since 2025. She is a member of the Delaware Senate representing the 5th district since 2021. ==References== ==Other websites== *Campaign website Category:1980s births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Wilmington, Delaware Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
